==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Topmost
<hw>Top"most`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Highest; uppermost;
<as>as, the <ex>topmost</ex> cliff; the <ex>topmost</ex> branch of a
tree</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The nightngale may claim the <qex>topmost</qex> bough.</q>
<rj><qau>Cowper.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Topographer</ent>⟦br⟧
